Interface TransformationPluginModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.inject.Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HrestsTransformationPlugin, OwlsTransformationPlugin, SawsdlTransformationPlugin, SwaggerTransformationPlugin, WSCTransformationPluginModule

    public interface TransformationPluginModule
extends com.google.inject.Module
    TransformationPluginModule defines a Module devoted to transforming service descriptions. This class is only really necessary to guide the service loader to detect implementations at runtime.
